<HEADLINE>
<P>
PROTEST DISRUPTS BUSH'S SPEECH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
My heartfelt thanks and appreciation go out to the protesters. Bush deserves to 
be embarrassed for his decadent policies which are shaped by fear rather than 
reality. 
</P>
<P>
We are talking to you, Mr. President. Please listen. 
</P>
<P>
MARK SHIFFLETT 
</P>
<P>
Mission Viejo 
</P>
</TEXT>
