Redlands 103, Antelope Valley 68 -- The Antelopes (21-6) were eliminated by 
host Redlands in a 5-AA Division game. 
</P>
<P>
Simi Valley 59, Fountain Valley 58 -- Three free throws in the final 24 seconds 
helped Simi Valley win its 5-AA playoff game at Fountain Valley. 
</P>
<P>
Despite a final-second, three-point basket by Fountain Valley's Derrick 
Corcoran, Tim Jaqua's free throw in the final 10 seconds clinched the game for 
Simi Valley. 
</P>
<P>
"We'll take the win and get out of here as quick as we can," Simi Valley Coach 
Dean Bradshaw said. 
</P>
<P>
Simi Valley's Steve Carnes had 23 points and five assists and Mike Wawryk had 
23 points and 11 rebounds. 
</P>
<P>
The Pioneers advance to the quarterfinals Tuesday where they meet Long Beach 
Poly, a 65-51 winner over Fountain Valley. 
</P>
