Burroughs 78, Redondo 55 -- The Indians hit 17 of 18 free throws en route to a 
4-A victory at Burroughs. 
</P>
<P>
Center Ray Velasquez was 10 of 15 from the field for 22 points and pulled down 
10 rebounds as the Indians improved to 17-6. 
