Highland Hall, which trailed by 10 points in the third quarter but outscored 
its opponent, 27-9, in the fourth quarter. 
</P>
<P>
John Klejnot grabbed 15 rebounds for Highland Hall, which won its 19th 
consecutive game and plays in the quarterfinals against Bethel Christian of 
Lancaster, which beat New Life, 107-73. 
