<DATELINE>
<P>
GOURA 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
son High School, employing an overpowering inside attack, defeated Agoura, 
67-51, in a 4-AA playoff game Friday at Agoura. 
</P>
<P>
Bill Martineau had 20 points and 11 rebounds to lead Edison (19-8). Brandon 
Jessie added 16 points and seven rebounds. Agoura (14-9) was held to a 
season-low 14 rebounds. 
</P>
<P>
