<TEXT>
<P>
Cathedral High School guard Paul Gonzales' 10-foot shot from the baseline with 
eight seconds remaining bounced off the rim, and Whittier Christian held on for 
a 68-66 victory in a 2-AA playoff game at Cathedral. 
</P>
<P>
Joe Kostantarakis led the Heralds (14-11) with 23 points and 10 rebounds, and 
Rueben Oronoz (14 points, 19 rebounds) and Dan Long (16 points, 15 rebounds) 
helped Whittier Christian. 
</P>
