35-34, at the half and outscored Capistrano Valley Christian, 23-14, in the 
third quarter. Rodarmel missed most of the third quarter after picking up his 
fourth foul early in the second half. 
</P>
<P>
St. Margaret's 63, Avalon 52 -- Junior center Ryan Westendorf scored 26 points 
and had 21 rebounds to lead St. Margaret's (19-4) at Long Beach Wilson. Dann 
Campaigne added 13 points and eight assists, and Jeff Hilgers scored 12 points 
and grabbed 11 rebounds for St. Margaret's. It was St. Margaret's 16th 
consecutive victory. 
