<P>
Photo, Mchelle Webb, left, of Foothill makes one of her 22 saves in helping the 
Knights upset Trabuco Hills, 2-0, in a 3-A playoff match. HENRY DiROCCO / For 
The Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
