INSURANCE FRAUD; WELFARE FRAUD; BRIBERY; RACKETEER INFLUENCED AND CORRUPT 
ORGANIZATIONS ACT; FUGITIVES; LABORATORIES; SMUSHKEVICH, MICHAEL; SMUSHKEVICH, 
DAVID 
