EDUCATION; TEACHERS -- LOS ANGELES; AFFORDABLE HOUSING; LOS ANGELES -- 
DEVELOPMENT AND REDEVELOPMENT; UNIVERSITY OF CALIFORNIA AT LOS ANGELES; 
WILDLIFE REFUGES 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
