PETE; FEINSTEIN, DIANNE; VAN DE KAMP, JOHN K; CALIFORNIA -- ELECTIONS -- 1990; 
POLITICAL CANDIDATES; POLITICAL CAMPAIGNS; CAPITAL PUNISHMENT; CRIME -- 
CALIFORNIA; INITIATIVES -- CALIFORNIA; CALIFORNIA -- POLITICS; SENTENCING 
