Administration Building on last day of housing policy protest. ; Photo, Student 
protesters dance at shantytown in celebration of what they called a victory 
against the university's "marrieds-only" housing policy. DON TORMEY / Los 
Angeles Times; Photo, UCI student reaches for tent as gust of wind hastens 
dismantling job. ; Photo, Senior Sheldon Forrest helps dismantle cardboard 
village occupied for 10 days. 
</P>
