ART EXHIBITS; BUILDINGS; REMODELING; HUNTINGTON BEACH ART CENTER; DESIGN; 
ARCHITECTURE 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA021790-0156 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 178391 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
February 17, 1990, Saturday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Orange County Life; Part N; Page 1; Column 5 
</P>
</SECTION>
